<!-- Section 4.6.7 Floating-point Rounding and Conversion instructions. P 159 - 166 -->

# Floating Convert with round Signed Doubleword to Single-Precision format

X-Form

* fcfids  FRT,FRB (Rc=0)
* fcfids. FRT,FRB (Rc=1)

Pseudo-code:

    FRT <- INT2FP(FRB, 'sint2single')

Special Registers Altered:

    FPRF FR FI
    FX XX
    CR1        (if Rc=1)
